description.en:
Doraemon Inu is an anime token with a solid community growth. Launched with 0 telegram members, with an organic growth and an active community.
Doraemon Inu has its own game that can be played on the website. With a leaderboard, we aim to compensate the best players. Also a buyback system that will help the growth of the token marketcap!
There is a lot of plans for the future. Don’t miss the ride!
